	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratiam et pacem a domino.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Impetrastis, quod petistis<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Der Zürcher Rat stimmte am 16. Dezember der von <placeName ref="place97">Basel</placeName> vorgeschlagenen Änderung des Schreibens an <persName ref="person138">Luther</persName> zu; vgl. oben <ref target="file10968">Nr. 926</ref>, 1 -26, und WA Briefwechsel XII 244.</note>, quia haec, quae nunc reddidistis, multo sunt circumspectiora (ut non fuerit <persName ref="person114">Leoni</persName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName ref="person114">Leo Jud</persName>.</note> et mihi grave in ipsa consentire ipsaque recipere), quam fuerint priora<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Siehe oben <ref target="file10966">Nr. 924</ref>.</note>.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cum libere mecum agis et mones, non est, quod praefari pergas et veluti deprecari culpam.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Libenter recipio fratrum liberas admonitiones.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuum erit curare, ne quid insciis <placeName ref="place121">Bernensibus</placeName> fiat<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Die auch im Schreiben Zürichs an <placeName ref="place97">Basel</placeName> ausdrücklich genannte Bedingung scheint nicht erfüllt worden zu sein; s. WA Briefwechsel XII 244.</note>.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="manual">Non iam dico fratres, hoc est verbi ministros, sed senatores.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nolunt isti se praeterin.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Faxit dominus, ut induratus <persName ref="person138">Lutheri</persName> suorumque animus nos ferat, nob iam dicere, nostra recipiat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fratres Argentinenses satis acerbe agunt cum Constantiensibus<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Vgl. <persName ref="person263">Zwicks</persName> Bericht vom 30. November (oben <ref target="file10963">Nr. 921</ref>, 27-58).</note>.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ibi nunc <persName ref="person20">Thomas Blaurerus</persName> consul designatus est.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nolunt isti sic compelli ad subscriptionem; ea libertate uti volunt, qua vident ecclesias Helveticas esse usas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nollem autem, quis apud nostros sciret, quam promptis animis ad rem tam exilem discessionem a nobis minitemini<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Vgl. oben <ref target="file10966">Nr. 924</ref>, 20-22, und 926, 20f.</note>.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Libere, quod sentio, dicam.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non potui non commoveri, et etiamnum commoveor.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nec scio, quid fecisset senatus, nisi <persName ref="person114">Leo</persName> et ego summis conatibus egissemus negotium.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si vel tantillum huius percepissent, nescio, quid actum esset.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nosti nostra ingenia.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Obsecro, eum vobis erga nos animum habetote inditum, qualem videtis nos erga vos gerere.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mors nulla nos dividet.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Et tamen scio iactare quosdam <placeName ref="place97">Basileienses</placeName> in solidum consentire, reliquos non item<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Vgl. oben <ref target="file10963">Nr. 921</ref>, 7f.</note>.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Invenias, qui dicant: "Utinam non recipiat <persName ref="person138">Lutherus</persName> id responsi!</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Priusquam enim <placeName ref="place97">Basileienses</placeName> istum offenderint, recipient<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a">recipient <hi>korrigiert aus</hi> receperint.</note> articulos adeoque subscribent<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b">subscribent <hi>korrigiert aus</hi> subscripserint.</note>.</s>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sic autem findemus, quos hactenus vidimus coniunctissimos."</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="manual">Haec tibi in sinum.</s>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nosti me.</s>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nosti, quali sim erga vos animo praeditus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iam vale et schedulam hanc<note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8">Nicht erhalten.</note> <persName ref="person81">Gryneo</persName> dato, ut mihi respondeat, qualia sint folia anabuli<note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9">Ein Pflanzenname; vgl. Mittellateinisches Wörterbuch bis zum ausgehenden 13. Jahrhundert, Bd. I, München 1967, Sp. 604 (anabulla).</note>.</s>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutem illi ex me dicito et reliquis fratribus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="29" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person28">Bucero</persName> has<note xml:id="fn10" type="footnote" n="10">Das am 13. Dezember in einem Brief Bullingers an <persName ref="person226">Vadian</persName> angekündigte Schreiben an <persName ref="person28">Bucer</persName> ist nicht erhalten (vgl. oben <ref target="file10969">Nr. 927</ref>, 24).</note> deferri curato.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="30" xml:lang="la" type="auto">16. decembris 1536.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="31" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus H. Bullingerus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="32" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo viro d. <persName ref="person154">Osvaldo Myconio</persName>, <placeName ref="place97">Basileien[sium]</placeName> antistiti vigilantissimo, suo in domino fratri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
